data.description: Well cared for family home with open floor plan for entertaining or just plain family fun!  Downstairs you will find a living room/flex room when you enter the home.  The kitchen is huge with lots of cabinets and counter space for the gourmet cook.  A large pantry will hold an abundant amount of goods.  The kitchen also has a bar that will easily seat 4 - 6 people.  The kitchen also overlooks the large dining area and great room, as well as the screened back porch and fenced backyard.  A half bath and study or hobby room is also on the first floor.  Upstairs, you will find the MBR, laundry room, 3 additional bedrooms and another full bath.  Close to schools, library, grocery store, lots of shopping and restaurants!  Easy to show!Washer, dryer & refrigerator will convey.  Ring doorbell and cameras will also convey.
